<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>AP credit is granted to students who receive a grade of 3 or higher on the respective tests.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.peace.edu/academics/academic-catalog" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

